response.overview: GCW present War Ready on FITE from Shinkiba 1stRING, Tokyo Japan. The first matches are already announced and two titles will be on the line - GCW Ultraviolent Title and GCW Tag Team. Check the lineup below:  Joey Janela vs Toshiyuki Sakuda  GCW Tag Team Title Match  Mega Bastards (Alex Colon & John Wayne Murdoch) (c) vs Jun Kasai & Masashi Takeda  Tag Team Match  Daisuke Sasaki & Yuko Miyamoto vs Cole Radrick & Toru Sugiura  GCW Ultraviolent Title Match  Rina Yamashita (c) vs Shlak
response.title: GCW War Ready 2022
